21:00.260 --> 21:03.127
Come on. We've been through this
a million times.

21:03.129 --> 21:05.263
Everything you need to know
about Lao ban Santa

21:05.265 --> 21:06.731
is right here in these binders.

21:06.733 --> 21:09.400
Okay, so he comes...

21:09.402 --> 21:10.301
She.

21:10.303 --> 21:12.637
Right.

21:12.639 --> 21:15.539
She comes on December 23rd,
the Eve of Christmas Eve...

21:15.541 --> 21:16.807
Yes.

21:16.809 --> 21:19.076
In a leased lebaron because...?

21:19.078 --> 21:20.945
It's better for her taxes.

21:20.947 --> 21:23.814
Well, why doesn't she just buy
a truck and use that every year?

21:23.816 --> 21:25.383
Wouldn't that make more sense?

21:25.385 --> 21:27.251
Louis, when a tradition
has been established,

21:27.253 --> 21:29.520
you really shouldn't try
to improve on it.
